FHS Mariachi Advance to State 


February 20, 2020 
– Falfurrias High School Mariachi advances to the UIL State Marching Contest to be held at the the UTRGV Performing Arts Complex. Mariachi Azahar earned a 1st division at UIL Solo and Ensemble on February 6.

 Item Link 







FHS Marching Band State Bound 

November 6, 2019 
– The Falfurrias High School Marching Band has the honor of competing at the 2019 UIL State Marching Championships at the Alamodome in San Antonio, Texas.

 Item Link 







FHS Powerlifting Team State Champions 

March 2018- The FHS Boys Powerlifting Team are the 2018 Class 3A State Champions. 
